<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kap lo thei ka hi puoi, Aw ka lungdeihte kha,
 Nungtieng lam sul bang a hei kit ta puou;
 Pielgal van sang saulun a kai zo tau,
 Nungsul hei talo in.

[V2]
 Ka kap khawvel gam zau ahin,
 Buolna gam tawha suihlung hel ni hin;
 Malai nung tieng ngaiin ka mau,
 Atho kit sek ngaihlai ni haw cheng khah

[V3]
 2. Suihlung ahel lunglai nemte sul bang heilo,
 Nau bang kahna a sauta luoi Lalpa;
 A lennau leh a meluh muh ka nuom,
 Angel dungsun a hiu.

[V4]
 3. Zion lim thing bang bel hehpih lungdeihte tawh,
 Galmuonna tang chunga lengin zai awi
 Ka ngaklah ie zie gam hawih achun Aw
 Laituol lengkhawm ung kau</lyrics>
<title>Kap Lothei Ka Hi Puoi!</title>
<hymn_number>286</hymn_number>
<author>Saihnuna</author>
</song>